## 5. Development Workflow

### Local Development Setup

**Option A: Separate Processes**
```bash
# Terminal 1 - Backend
cd src/backend
dotnet watch run --project API

# Terminal 2 - Frontend
cd src/frontend
npm run dev
```

**Option B: Docker Compose (Recommended)**
